<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="000_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯嗯，<delay20 />你們想要拍攝結婚紀念的照片啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是拍照的話，<delay8 />
是可以使用我的攝影棚沒錯<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="000_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
攝影場景<delay8 />該怎麼布置才好呢？<delay40 />
這個要我們自己準備，<delay8 />似乎有點困難欸<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔喔！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！
你來得正好！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有點事情想拜託你<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_00" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔喔！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！
你來得正好！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有點事情想拜託你<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00">這位<colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是一對非常恩愛的夫妻，<delay frames="30" />
他們想拍攝結婚紀念照片。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道，<delay20 />說到六月<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會想到六月新娘嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每年到了這個時期，<delay20 />
他們都會拍照留念喔。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="01 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是有一個問題<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我可以把攝影棚借出來，<delay20 />
但卻沒有人來搭建最重要的場景。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以呢！<delay20 />我想請你幫忙
搭建婚禮攝影的場景！<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想請你做的事，<delay20 />
就是把婚禮攝影場景必要的家具<delay20 />
擺放在適合拍照的位置。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我這邊會準備好<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />場景需要的家具，<delay8 />你不用擔心！<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概就是這樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
怎麼樣？<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以麻煩你嗎？</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />交給我吧！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真拿你沒辦法啊</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的嗎？！<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不會忘記你的大恩大德的！<10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我馬上去準備！<delay20 />
來，快進去<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />攝影棚！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡就是婚禮攝影專用的攝影棚了！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />雖然只是換了<delay8 />
裡面房間的壁紙跟地板……<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是第一次使用攝影棚吧。<delay20 />
我簡單說明一下使用方法。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想改變攝影棚的場景時，<delay20 />
就當成是<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己的房子，<delay20 />
用<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />自由地更改布置吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟<colour id="1" />Nook購物<colour id="65535" />簽下了租約，<delay8 />
家具跟雜貨都可以<delay20 />
拿來當場景的裝飾品<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要是刊登在
<tag a="110" b="1" /><colour id="1" />目錄<colour id="65535" />上的東西，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都可以立刻拿來裝飾！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使用方法跟平常的攝影棚一樣。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前已經跟<tag a="110" b="1" />
說明過了，<delay8 />這次就不再多說了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就待在外面，<delay20 />
如果你忘了使用方法，<delay8 />
可以<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨時來問我。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，對了對了！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可以中途離開房間，<delay20 />
要繼續的時候就來跟我說一聲吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />具體上要做的事以及詳細的情況，<delay8 />
都可以問<colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />就拜託你囉！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
你來了！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="04 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要幫<colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
拍攝婚禮照片嗎？<delay40 />
還是要問<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於攝影棚的事？</message>
	<message label="010_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">幫忙拍攝婚禮照片</message>
	<message label="010_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於攝影棚</message>
	<message label="010_c" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒事了</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔喔！謝謝你！<delay20 />
你要來幫忙拍攝婚禮照片啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼<delay8 />我去準備，<delay8 />你稍等一下。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="08 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想問關於什麼呢？</message>
	<message label="012_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於場景</message>
	<message label="012_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於模特兒</message>
	<message label="012_c" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於服裝</message>
	<message label="012_d" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於拍照</message>
	<message label="012_e" attrib="00 00 00 00">不用了</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想用攝影棚，<delay20 />
可以隨意使用，沒關係的。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想拍攝
<colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />的婚禮照片，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就來跟我說吧。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔！<delay8 />辛苦了！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來你已經順利拍好照片了呢。
</message>
	<message label="014_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以的話，<delay20 />
明天也過來幫忙吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，<delay8 />但還是要麻煩你了。</message>
	<message label="014_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天六月就要結束了，<delay20 />
聽說他們兩個明天也要回去了，<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得變冷清了呢。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />真是超棒的派對！<delay20 />
我借出自己的攝影棚
也是值得的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜託你真是選對人了！<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！辛苦了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經變成<delay8 />搭建場景的專家了。<delay8 />
哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="017_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常謝謝你的幫忙！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小小心意，<delay8 />不成敬意！</message>
	<message label="017_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就收下吧！<delay20 />
這是<colour id="1" />婚禮柵欄<colour id="65535" />的ＤＩＹ方程式！</message>
	<message label="017_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是想這樣做的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你的包包好像滿了，<delay8 />我沒辦法給你<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你整理好持有物品之後，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來跟我說一聲，我再交給你吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，<delay8 />對你的感謝三言兩語表達不盡！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎隨時再過來玩喔！</message>
	<message label="017_04" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
你來拿<delay8 />我剛剛沒能給你的禮物啊！<10_4 />
這是<colour id="1" />婚禮柵欄<colour id="65535" />的ＤＩＹ方程式喔！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />我也想像健兆那樣<delay8 />
輕輕鬆鬆<delay8 />就能製作出來，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但對我來講還是太難了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這麼聰明，應該沒問題的！<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要製作看看喔！</message>
	<message label="018_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />什麼？<delay20 />
你也不知道怎麼<colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ<colour id="65535" />嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
這可真傷腦筋啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />對了！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽說有人在舉辦<delay8 />
<colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ工作坊<colour id="65535" />喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要去<colour id="1" />服務處<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
找<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />商量一下？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />機會難得，<delay8 />我也去學一下好了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="04 00 00 00">對了，<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你今天也要幫<colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
拍攝婚禮照片嗎？<delay40 />
還是要問<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於攝影棚的事？</message>
	<message label="019_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">幫忙拍攝婚禮照片</message>
	<message label="019_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">關於攝影棚</message>
	<message label="019_c" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒事了</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀哎呀，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感謝你<delay8 />上個月幫我
搭建婚禮攝影的場景！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
一臉滿足地回去了。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這都是託你的福！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />回去了。<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他們很高興，<delay8 />
還說「拍到好照片，真是太好了」。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<tag a="110" b="1" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />莉詠<colour id="65535" />跟<colour id="3" />健兆<colour id="65535" />回去了。<delay20 />
畢竟六月新娘的時期也結束了。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
恩愛的夫妻<delay8 />真好啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望他們永遠幸福快樂<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
</msbt>